Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.15,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BAKTI
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:23.91,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,JANGAN KHAWATIRKAN AKU, PERGILAH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.96,0:13:42.22,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,IKUTI PRIA YANG KAMU CINTAI
